<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/faq.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>

    <main class="faq-page">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="faq-content">
                <h1>How to Register for NASCON Events</h1>
                
                <section class="faq-section">
                    <h2>Registration Process</h2>
                    <ol>
                        <li>Create an account on the NASCON website</li>
                        <li>Log in to your account</li>
                        <li>Browse available events in the Events section</li>
                        <li>Click on the event you want to register for</li>
                        <li>Click the "Register Now" button</li>
                        <li>Complete the registration form</li>
                        <li>Make the payment if required</li>
                        <li>Receive confirmation email</li>
                    </ol>
                </section>

                <section class="faq-section">
                    <h2>Important Notes</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Early registration is recommended as events may fill up quickly</li>
                        <li>Some events may have prerequisites or eligibility criteria</li>
                        <li>Team events require all team members to register individually</li>
                        <li>Keep your registration confirmation email for reference</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section class="faq-section">
                    <h2>Need Help?</h2>
                    <p>If you encounter any issues during registration, please contact our support team:</p>
                    <ul class="contact-info">
                        <li><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> support@nascon.com</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> +92-51-1234567</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> FAST-NUCES, H-11/4, A-K Brohi Road, Islamabad</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> Monday - Friday: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html> 